subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Ivanovic of Serbia, who entered the Australian Open as a favorite after reaching the finals of the Brisbane Open the week before, lost in the first round to Lucie Hradecka of the Czech Republic.
